if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好假囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係澳洲讀書果陣 homestay媽媽同我講架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢呃鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好享受早餐時間<br />\n但又要求奇夾下野就食得 好快就搞得掂<br />\n<br />\n用下腦啦"},{"pid":"7825cc93a1c06f79e6597f5e18580eafe2a103f1","tid":62450,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T00:17:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"adb97f567d8fe716e024070ac093d7d1c20e0a9c","tid":62450,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>識唔識架你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbreakfast讀bread first<br />\n唔會讀break同fast囉<br />\n所以係法文啲fd嚟架<br />\n叫你晨早流流食個包先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得呢位巴打啱D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger 應該唔係英文讀音黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFrench French嘅早餐係petit d&eacute;jeuner<br />\nQu&eacute;becois French嘅早餐係d&eacute;jeuner <br />\nD&eacute;jeuner就係d&eacute; (break) + jeuner (fast)<br />\n即係停止禁食，即係瞓完成晚冇食嘅第一餐<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提英文嘅dinner係嚟自法文嘅d&icirc;ner，舊時係lunch咁解，而家就得返Qu&eacute;becois French, Belgium French會咁用，而晚餐就會係souper，即係supper嘅word root<br />\n<br />\n利申：識啲啲法文，住喺法文區"},{"pid":"b71e43d41d014b631c4403fa618808d0e1b21ede","tid":62450,"uid":24739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T17:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑撚死，明明個解釋係岩，但因為係耶撚講所以唔撚信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"